abstract: Car bombing in Ameen, Shiite suburb of Baghdad, kills at least 12 and wounds 42 more; Sunni Muslims working with Islamic State are known to target area, but no one immediately claims responsibility.
lead_paragraph: A car bomb killed at least 12 people and injured 42 others on Monday in Ameen.

headline.print_headline: Middle East; Iraq: Deadly Bombing Strikes Baghdad
